729452f-b.title: Richmond: Richmond Terrace - Alaska Street
729452f-b.text:
Richmond Terrace, south side, between Alaska Street and
Tompkins Court, showing the Protestant Episcopal Church of the
Ascension. Adjoining the church on the right is the Staten
Island Cemetery; on the left is the parish house. The view is
aoross a pond from the Staten Psland Railroad freight yards.
April 1930
P. L. Sperr
